The time has come for us to find the undiscovered talent, to hear the old voice of culture, to know the true story of Jakarta... Live from Telkom University, here comes the FIRST and biggest event of UKM Betawie. "PAGELARAN BETAWIE 2016"

Come and Feel the Soul and be the first to see with your eyes the true Color of Betawie Culture.
